    section(id='feature' title='Feature')

        h1 Want to be Featured Here?

        p.
            NCAS partnered groups are verified and vetted anthropomorphic groups operating in or serving the North
            Carolina community. All partnered groups must have clear rules and moderation practices, a
            SFW (minor-friendly) space, and a reputation for maintaining and supporting their services.

        p.
            Are you a representative of a group that wants to be featured here? We would love to work with you! Please
            send us an email at #[a(href='mailto:community@ncanthrosociety.org') community@ncanthrosociety.org] to start
            the process. Your email should include:
        ul
            li A description of your group that we can use on our website and in promotions.
            li An image we can use on our website and in promoting your group.
            li The geographical region your group serves.
            li Links to your group‚Äôs rules, code of conduct, terms of service, etc.
            li Links to your group‚Äôs social media, chats, website, and other spaces you would like to be featured.

        p.
            If approved, your partnered group may also request for NCAS to advertise your group and its events and even
            for support in hosting and running events.
